Package: amcModels
Title: Absorbing Markov Chain Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Brigham", "Halverson", , "brighamhalverson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The main functionality is to fit one of three absorbing Markov chain models. Using a nonhierarchical approach with no grouping. A hierarchical approach to gain inference on transition probabilities between subgroups. Finally to fit a hierarchical model with a random partioning step to combine groupings.
